  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01891', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-104-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '某一線徑1.6m/m之電線1Km長之電阻值為8.931Ω，熱阻抗為415，若周遭溫度為25℃，當此電線通 過27安培時，其芯線溫度（℃）為何？', '["27℃", "52℃", "66℃", "71℃"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "38e3f80b9c13", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2d8949dd1c15", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104060", "c": "402", "s": "0707", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門驗船師引水人第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01892', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-104-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種電氣火災原因，易於濕度較高場所之電器用具發生？', '["斷路", "導電", "半斷線", "積污導電"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "38e3f80b9c13", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2d8949dd1c15", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104060", "c": "402", "s": "0707", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門驗船師引水人第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01893', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-104-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據日本學者矢島安雄氏等之調查研究結果，有關火災與氣象之影響關係的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["愈接近地面處之反象氣層，對減低火勢之延燒力，最為有效", "風速若超過13m/sec時，上風之延燒速度幾近於零", "風速若超過16m/sec時，飛火距離與風速成反比", "風速在5m/sec以下者，其下風之延燒速度約為上風之4～5倍，風側之速度較下風稍快，但差別不大"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "38e3f80b9c13", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2d8949dd1c15", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104060", "c": "402", "s": "0707", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門驗船師引水人第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01894', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-104-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關閃燃（flashover）現象之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["易發生在通風不良的居室，熱容易蓄積", "是成長期發展至全盛期之短時間現象", "熱煙層之熱不穩定是導致閃燃之原因", "火焰竄出門口是觀察指標之一"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "38e3f80b9c13", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2d8949dd1c15", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104060", "c": "402", "s": "0707", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專門驗船師引水人第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
